<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1203071>
    dc:description "FIGURE59. Caligus triabdominalis Byrnes, 1987, female. A, habitus, dorsal; B, antenna, post-antennal processand maxillule drawn in situ; C, sternal furca; D, endopod of leg 2; E, outer margin spines on exopodof leg2; F, exopodof leg 3; G, exopodof leg 4. Scale bars:1.0 mm on A, 100 µm on B, C, 50 µm on D–F, 200 µm on G." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1203071/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

